[{"Code":"en","Title":"How payment sessions work","Slug":"how-payment-sessions-work","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mhn7l79r-txnv64-001\" style=\"text-align:start;line-height:24px;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Inter;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\">A <strong>Payment Session</strong> is a streamlined, Xendit-hosted solution designed to simplify payment collection and payment method management with minimal integration effort. It acts as a secure, <a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/docs/pci-dss-compliance?highlight=saq\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">PCI-compliant</a> bridge that allows businesses to facilitate one-time payments, save customer payment details for future use, or perform both actions simultaneously through a single flow. See supported flow <a href=\"https://docs.xendit.co/docs/supported-use-cases-1\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">here</a>.</p><p data-block-id=\"mknjr7e6-8rmzdc-005\" style=\"text-align:start;line-height:24px;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Inter;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\"><img data-block-id=\"mknjrmpu-myaolf-007\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(189).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mhn7l79r-txnv64-001\" style=\"text-align:start;line-height:24px;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Inter;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mhn7l79r-txnv64-001\" style=\"text-align:start;line-height:24px;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Inter;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\">Depending on the desired user experience and technical capacity, businesses can implement Payment Sessions either via a <a href=\"/v1/docs/how-payment-sessions-work#payment-link\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Payment Link</strong></a>, which redirects customers to a ready-to-use Xendit checkout page, or through <a href=\"/v1/docs/how-payment-sessions-work#xendit-components\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Xendit Components</strong></a>, which embeds secure payment fields directly into an existing website or app for a native, branded feel.</p><blockquote data-block-id=\"mkjqal1z-105nnf-029\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\" style=\"background:rgb(221, 247, 255);border-left:4px solid rgb(0, 106, 138);overflow:auto;\"><p data-block-id=\"mkjq9f49-2jb3io-028\" style=\"text-align:start;line-height:24px;box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Inter;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\">See <a href=\"https://demo-store.xendit.co/\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">Xendit Demo Store</a> to give you visualization of how it will interact with your store. </p></blockquote><h2 data-block-id=\"mjgtm5jq-pr6oeq-003\">Payment Link</h2><p data-block-id=\"mhn7mg57-lz8ll4-057\">Payment Link interfaces provide a ready-to-use checkout page hosted by Xendit.</p><p data-block-id=\"mhn7n5wc-tyctju-064\"><img data-block-id=\"mkm3u8fv-0emvcg-041\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(188).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><h4 data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh1-nk67km-043\" data-start=\"2073\" data-end=\"2089\">How it works</h4><ol data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-utvd2j-044\" start=\"1\" data-start=\"2091\" data-end=\"2301\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-b5g2g2-045\" data-start=\"2091\" data-end=\"2135\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-ut9pig-046\" data-start=\"2094\" data-end=\"2135\">You create a Payment Session via the API or Xendit Dashboard (coming soon)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-purlcs-047\" data-start=\"2136\" data-end=\"2180\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-tx6yb2-048\" data-start=\"2139\" data-end=\"2180\">Xendit returns a unique Payment Link URL.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-b1t5bp-049\" data-start=\"2181\" data-end=\"2239\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-avvj6m-050\" data-start=\"2184\" data-end=\"2239\">You redirect your customer to the hosted checkout page.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-rt1z84-051\" data-start=\"2240\" data-end=\"2301\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-gzn5n6-052\" data-start=\"2243\" data-end=\"2301\">Xendit handles the full payment experience and processing.</p></li></ol><h4 data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-hq9kiv-053\" data-start=\"2303\" data-end=\"2322\">User experience</h4><ul data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-tzy4k0-054\" data-start=\"2324\" data-end=\"2497\"><li data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-7omnha-055\" data-start=\"2324\" data-end=\"2387\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-xyucof-056\" data-start=\"2326\" data-end=\"2387\">Customers are redirected to a <strong>Xendit-hosted checkout page</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-bn1915-057\" data-start=\"2388\" data-end=\"2446\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-4xj6ek-058\" data-start=\"2390\" data-end=\"2446\">No checkout UI needs to be designed or maintained by you</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-fl3m78-059\" data-start=\"2447\" data-end=\"2497\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-5g57sl-060\" data-start=\"2449\" data-end=\"2497\">Optimized for conversion and security by default</p></li></ul><h4 data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-ebk51k-061\" data-start=\"2499\" data-end=\"2524\">Why use Payment Link?</h4><ul data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-4woiqh-062\" data-start=\"2526\" data-end=\"2815\"><li data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-6175dd-063\" data-start=\"2526\" data-end=\"2609\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh2-5kwmwo-064\" data-start=\"2528\" data-end=\"2609\">Lowest development effort</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh3-qnmsus-066\" data-start=\"2611\" data-end=\"2704\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh3-8d62rn-067\" data-start=\"2613\" data-end=\"2704\">No UI or compliance burden - Xendit hosts and secures the entire checkout experience.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh3-4usbl3-069\" data-start=\"2706\" data-end=\"2815\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsfmh3-eqi2vr-070\" data-start=\"2708\" data-end=\"2815\">Best for quick integration - Ideal if you want to accept payments without building a custom checkout.</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mjgu5cwo-onnxmj-046\">Follow this link for more detailed <a href=\"/v1/docs/payment-sessions-overview\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">integration guide</a></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mjgtmb2e-8pk2wa-004\">Xendit Components </h2><p data-block-id=\"mjgunm6k-uaus36-074\">Xendit Components lets you embed Xendit’s secure payment fields directly into your own website or mobile application.</p><p data-block-id=\"mjpry3kt-mt13tt-020\"><img data-block-id=\"mkm388mw-y3qbo4-015\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(187).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mjguy1c6-bdg3ya-085\" data-path-to-node=\"16,0,0\">Components Mode uses Xendit Components SDK to render secure, PCI-compliant payment fields (such as card number, expiry date, and CVV) inside your existing checkout UI. Customers stay on your site throughout the payment flow.</p><h4 data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdq-8lbizt-106\" data-start=\"3287\" data-end=\"3303\">How it works</h4><ol data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdq-v0ob19-107\" start=\"1\" data-start=\"3305\" data-end=\"3537\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdq-at4vcf-108\" data-start=\"3305\" data-end=\"3349\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdq-wlpdqb-109\" data-start=\"3308\" data-end=\"3349\">You create a Payment Session via the API.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdq-496tv2-110\" data-start=\"3350\" data-end=\"3390\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdq-ardkzc-111\" data-start=\"3353\" data-end=\"3390\">You integrate Xendit Components SDK.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdq-webz03-112\" data-start=\"3391\" data-end=\"3454\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdq-zhi98i-113\" data-start=\"3394\" data-end=\"3454\">You mount secure payment components into your checkout form.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-zefput-114\" data-start=\"3455\" data-end=\"3537\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-6dyhrp-115\" data-start=\"3458\" data-end=\"3537\">Customers enter payment details and complete payment without leaving your site.</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-zwwbhx-116\" data-start=\"3539\" data-end=\"3627\">Xendit securely handles sensitive payment data and payment processing behind the scenes.</p><h4 data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-nuvzk3-117\" data-start=\"3629\" data-end=\"3648\">User experience</h4><ul data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-di7x5x-118\" data-start=\"3650\" data-end=\"3803\"><li data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-oomutm-119\" data-start=\"3650\" data-end=\"3697\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-ztnmkd-120\" data-start=\"3652\" data-end=\"3697\">Customers never leave your website or app</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-okub75-121\" data-start=\"3698\" data-end=\"3759\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-umb5sa-122\" data-start=\"3700\" data-end=\"3759\">Payment fields feel like a native part of your checkout</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-fydnzp-123\" data-start=\"3760\" data-end=\"3803\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-ttnt3k-124\" data-start=\"3762\" data-end=\"3803\">Fully aligned with your brand and UI flow</p></li></ul><h4 data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-5hnz1a-125\" data-start=\"3805\" data-end=\"3833\">Why use Xendit Components?</h4><ul data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-1xux43-126\" data-start=\"3835\" data-end=\"4135\"><li data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-fty6zd-127\" data-start=\"3835\" data-end=\"3912\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-9he0o0-128\" data-start=\"3837\" data-end=\"3912\">You control layout, styling, and surrounding UI consistently with your branding</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-qy5r56-130\" data-start=\"3914\" data-end=\"4013\"><p data-block-id=\"mjpsjzdr-x6vmai-131\" data-start=\"3916\" data-end=\"4013\">Secure by default - Xendit manages tokenization, and compliance (e.g. PCI DSS).</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mjqopm2l-exspl0-002\"></p>","SeoTitle":"How payment sessions work","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Cara kerja Payment Session","Slug":"how-payment-sessions-work","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mc27ggy9-mc1usq-001\">Titik akhir Payment Session baru kami dibuat untuk menyederhanakan proses pengumpulan dan pengelolaan informasi metode pembayaran untuk bisnis Anda. Fitur ini memanfaatkan halaman kami yang dihosting Xendit untuk menyimpan detail pembayaran pengguna akhir dengan aman, memungkinkan transaksi di masa mendatang dengan mudah.</p><p data-block-id=\"mc27gp5o-ulagjx-003\"><img data-block-id=\"mc27gp5o-l28l64-004\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(19).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(19).png\" width=\"453\" height=\"517\" dataalign=\"center\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:453px;height:517px;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align:start;line-height:1.33333;box-sizing:border-box;border:0 solid var(--color-border,currentColor);--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-inset:var(--tw-empty,/*!*/ /*!*/);--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(147,197,253,0.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;margin:1.428em 0px 1em;font-size:1.75em;font-weight:700;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;color:rgb(38, 38, 38);font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\" data-block-id=\"mc27gp5p-b0c550-005\" class=\"sl-link-heading sl-text-4xl sl-leading-tight sl-font-prose sl-font-bold sl-text-heading\" id=\"how-does-it-work\"><strong>Overview</strong></h2><p data-block-id=\"mc27gp5p-xkv89z-006\"><img data-block-id=\"mc27gp5p-9kj8sl-007\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Untitled diagram-2024-12-03-123511.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><h4 data-block-id=\"mc27gp5q-rr1w13-008\">Cara kerjanya:</h4><ol data-block-id=\"mc27gp5q-2bnf6s-009\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mc27gp5q-knhkms-010\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27gp5q-xnlpx4-011\">Jika pelanggan Anda setuju untuk menyimpan metode pembayaran mereka untuk tagihan di masa mendatang, buat <strong>API Payment Session</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc27gp5q-eatjjo-012\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27gp5q-eybwva-013\">Mengarahkan pelanggan ke <strong>URL link pembayaran</strong> yang disediakan dalam respons sesi</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc27gp5q-baas69-014\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27gp5q-62g74l-015\">Pelanggan memasukkan detail metode pembayaran mereka di halaman yang dihosting Xendit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc27gp5r-yj6lwp-016\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27gp5r-4e9eop-017\">Xendit mengirimkan <strong>webhook</strong> ke sistem Anda saat metode pembayaran berhasil ditautkan</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc27gp5r-zbrszz-018\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27gp5r-eqxkl7-019\">Simpan dari <code>Payment Token</code> webhook. Token ini akan digunakan untuk transaksi di masa mendatang</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc27gp5r-dmb8aj-020\"><p data-block-id=\"mc27gp5r-95t055-021\">Saat tiba waktunya untuk menagih pelanggan, picu Permintaan Pembayaran menggunakan yang tersimpan <code>Payment Token</code> (lihat <a href=\"/v1/docs/id/tokenization\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">panduan</a> ini )</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mc27gwb7-bw69ki-022\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Cara kerja Payment Session","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"วิธีการทำงานของเซสชันการชำระเงิน","Slug":"how-payment-sessions-work","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"2f2862c9-22ca-4658-a12f-34a895b0f321\">Payment Session endpoints ของเราเป็นโซลูชันเพื่อทำให้กระบวนการเก็บเงินหรือการจัดการข้อมูลวิธีการชำระเงินของผู้ใช้ปลายทางสำหรับธุรกิจของคุณง่ายขึ้น ฟีเจอร์นี้ใช้ประโยชน์จากหน้าเพจที่โฮสต์โดย Xendit เพื่อจัดเก็บรายละเอียดการชำระเงินของผู้ใช้ปลายทางอย่างปลอดภัย ช่วยให้สามารถทำธุรกรรมในอนาคตได้อย่างง่ายดาย</p><p data-block-id=\"f94ce33c-f510-445f-b5d1-73309cff6ff9\"><img data-block-id=\"d7a067e8-fcf5-449b-b180-ca3ec8bed449\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(19).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt title=\"image(19).png\" width=\"453\" height=\"517\" dataalign=\"center\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link newtab style=\"width:453px;height:517px;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align:start;line-height:1.33333;box-sizing:border-box;border:0 solid var(--color-border,currentColor);--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-inset:var(--tw-empty,/*!*/ /*!*/);--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(147,197,253,0.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;margin:1.428em 0px 1em;font-size:1.75em;font-weight:700;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;color:rgb(38, 38, 38);font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\" data-block-id=\"3359aed2-87e0-4a45-b7cb-1f06dee77506\" class=\"sl-link-heading sl-text-4xl sl-leading-tight sl-font-prose sl-font-bold sl-text-heading\" id=\"how-does-it-work\"><strong>ภาพรวมโซลูชัน</strong></h2><p data-block-id=\"d59640b6-5e90-4ba3-8048-8cd8b069a6fd\"><img data-block-id=\"647ff642-d876-477e-8a48-c90759dcc7f0\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Untitled diagram-2024-12-03-123511.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><h4 data-block-id=\"71e69fd0-833e-4aca-8f52-c7e4ae39972e\">วิธีการทำงาน:</h4><ol data-block-id=\"b72e53bf-a10e-4527-a478-8e812e552fde\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"bca1ad23-a78f-4b84-9c1a-631276c569a7\"><p data-block-id=\"00381c81-9d26-4326-8642-0cde96f31e5e\">เมื่อลูกค้าของคุณตกลงที่จะบันทึกวิธีการชำระเงินของตนสำหรับการเรียกเก็บเงินในอนาคต ให้สร้าง <strong>Payment Session API</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"b7ecc48d-91d8-4391-9a01-e1cb98485ad1\"><p data-block-id=\"e51deb38-ef95-4b12-8ffb-d6b14304f39b\">เปลี่ยนเส้นทางลูกค้าไปยัง <strong>payment link url</strong> ที่ให้ไว้ในการตอบกลับเซสชัน</p></li><li data-block-id=\"fdde03f5-458c-4992-a2b8-a307a5fdd392\"><p data-block-id=\"2284be67-2de7-43b1-a4f7-707eb5148175\">ลูกค้าป้อนรายละเอียดวิธีการชำระเงินของตนบนหน้าเพจที่โฮสต์โดย Xendit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"778bf047-029d-40cf-858d-9014e7118952\"><p data-block-id=\"8132937c-7381-4a58-a1b1-e7c3ea4e2533\">Xendit ส่ง <strong>webhook</strong> ไปยังระบบของคุณเมื่อวิธีการชำระเงินเชื่อมโยงสำเร็จ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"cb15486e-c8c4-4995-bcb8-d678f5033718\"><p data-block-id=\"a81ac303-8b13-44b9-804e-5311e1f5c7b0\">บันทึก <code>Payment Token</code> จาก webhook โทเค็นนี้จะถูกใช้สำหรับธุรกรรมในอนาคต</p></li><li data-block-id=\"cd7edda4-da6c-4ad9-892a-c090ef3c61cf\"><p data-block-id=\"0e76828b-fc6a-423d-a0ef-393bd1e2224f\">เมื่อถึงเวลาเรียกเก็บเงินจากลูกค้า ให้เรียกใช้ Payment Request โดยใช้ `Payment Token` ที่จัดเก็บไว้ (ดู <a href=\"/docs/pay-with-tokens\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">แนวทาง</a>นี้)</p></li></ol><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\" data-permitted-reader-groups=\"9f0df790-187b-4514-b1da-ec79a03a5322\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfvo6vv-tmei9l-003\"><strong>Payment Session</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvofw3-h2myck-006\"><strong>Payment Session API</strong> เป็นโซลูชันที่ง่ายขึ้นสำหรับการรับชำระเงินและการจัดการวิธีการชำระเงินของลูกค้าของคุณผ่าน <strong>Xendit-hosted checkout page</strong><br type=\"inline\">ช่วยให้คุณสามารถเก็บเงินแบบครั้งเดียวที่ลูกค้าอยู่ต่อหน้า หรือบันทึกวิธีการชำระเงินของลูกค้าอย่างปลอดภัยเพื่อใช้ในอนาคต โดยใช้ความพยายามในการผสานรวมน้อยที่สุด</p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvou0i-54nfqw-010\" data-start=\"539\" data-end=\"582\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvou0i-54nfqw-010\" data-start=\"539\" data-end=\"582\">Payment Session รองรับกรณีการใช้งานหลักสองกรณี:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mgfvou0i-pqnd65-011\" data-start=\"584\" data-end=\"768\"><li data-block-id=\"mgfvou0i-gd6plz-012\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\" data-start=\"584\" data-end=\"666\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfvou0j-opbimn-013\" data-start=\"586\" data-end=\"666\"><strong>One-Time Payment</strong> – เก็บเงินเพียงครั้งเดียวในขณะที่ลูกค้าอยู่ต่อหน้า</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfvou0j-efkvtz-014\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\" data-start=\"667\" data-end=\"768\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfvou0j-eoviec-015\" data-start=\"669\" data-end=\"768\"><strong>Save Payment Method</strong> – ให้ลูกค้าบันทึกวิธีการชำระเงินของตนอย่างปลอดภัยสำหรับธุรกรรมในอนาคต</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mgfvou0j-gva9zb-016\" data-start=\"770\" data-end=\"890\">Payment Sessions ทั้งหมดใช้ Xendit-hosted checkout page เพื่อให้มั่นใจถึงประสบการณ์ผู้ใช้ที่ปลอดภัย เป็นไปตามข้อกำหนด และสม่ำเสมอ</p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvqf26-koz0pn-017\" data-start=\"770\" data-end=\"890\"><img data-block-id=\"mgfvyxoz-f5xhhd-003\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(144).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvqkkd-arhbep-019\" data-start=\"770\" data-end=\"890\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvqkwc-qyekrz-020\" data-start=\"770\" data-end=\"890\"><strong>ภาพรวมโซลูชัน</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvr946-tnc0up-024\" data-start=\"770\" data-end=\"890\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvo6vv-humauj-004\"><img data-block-id=\"mgfvyxoz-s9pgr9-004\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(143).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfw1oa3-mbf1kx-009\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfw1oa3-mbf1kx-009\">Payment Session ทำให้การเก็บเงินและการจัดการวิธีการชำระเงินง่ายขึ้นผ่าน <strong>Xendit-hosted checkout page</strong> ขึ้นอยู่กับกรณีการใช้งานของคุณ โฟลว์อาจเป็นได้ทั้ง <strong>One-Time Payment</strong> หรือ <strong>Save Payment Method</strong></p><ol data-block-id=\"mgfw5jd6-u8ndr9-153\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7r-ij9dh9-123\" data-start=\"260\" data-end=\"449\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7r-eo8452-124\" data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"293\">สร้าง Payment Session จากเซิร์ฟเวอร์ของคุณสำหรับ One-Time Payment หรือ Save Payment Method เพื่อรับ <code data-start=\"433\" data-end=\"446\">payment_link_url</code> ของ Xendit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7r-ncs7jx-130\" data-start=\"451\" data-end=\"590\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7r-7h5ta8-131\" data-start=\"454\" data-end=\"477\">เปลี่ยนเส้นทางลูกค้าของคุณไปยังหน้าเพจที่โฮสต์โดย Xendit โดยใช้ <code data-start=\"521\" data-end=\"539\">payment_link_url</code></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7r-e9yayp-135\" data-start=\"592\" data-end=\"693\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7r-ggt4s7-136\" data-start=\"595\" data-end=\"616\">ลูกค้าจะป้อนรายละเอียดการชำระเงินและยืนยันธุรกรรมภายใน Xendit-hosted checkout page</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-2xvwla-140\" data-start=\"695\" data-end=\"1036\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-9g1xot-141\" data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"716\">โฟลว์การชำระเงิน</p><ul data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-ob0ftq-142\" data-start=\"720\" data-end=\"1036\"><li data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-09jkqi-143\" data-start=\"720\" data-end=\"868\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-qvy236-144\" data-start=\"722\" data-end=\"868\">One-Time Payment: Xendit ดำเนินการชำระเงินและส่ง webhook (<code data-start=\"794\" data-end=\"813\">payment.capture</code> หรือ <code data-start=\"817\" data-end=\"833\">payment.failed</code>) ระบบของคุณจะอัปเดตคำสั่งซื้อ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-nnxjb6-145\" data-start=\"872\" data-end=\"1036\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-aisudl-146\" data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"1036\">Save Payment Method: Xendit เชื่อมโยงวิธีการชำระเงินและส่ง webhook (<code data-start=\"952\" data-end=\"975\">payment_token.activation</code>) ระบบของคุณจะจัดเก็บ Payment Token สำหรับการเรียกเก็บเงินในอนาคต</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-4jsali-052\" data-start=\"1547\" data-end=\"1817\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-qtcags-053\" data-start=\"1550\" data-end=\"1605\"><mark class=\"f39082a8-8a72-4c8e-9612-3bd4ca32ecfb\" data-type=\"comment\" data-comment-id=\"f39082a8-8a72-4c8e-9612-3bd4ca32ecfb\">การเรียกเก็บเงินในอนาคต (ทางเลือกสำหรับ Save Payment Method)</mark></p><ul data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-8sfigl-054\" data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1817\"><li data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-7l72hb-055\" data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1708\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-ys9998-056\" data-start=\"1611\" data-end=\"1708\">เมื่อพร้อมที่จะเรียกเก็บเงินจากลูกค้า ให้สร้าง <a href=\"/docs/pay-with-tokens\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">Payment Request โดยใช้ Payment Token ที่จัดเก็บไว้</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-qcr2ig-057\" data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1817\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-t4xvda-058\" data-start=\"1714\" data-end=\"1817\">ลูกค้าไม่จำเป็นต้องป้อนรายละเอียดการชำระเงินซ้ำ ทำให้การชำระเงินแบบประจำหรือซ้ำง่ายขึ้น</p></li></ul></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-oqgse3-059\" data-start=\"1819\" data-end=\"2112\"><strong>ข้อควรทราบ</strong>: โฟลว์ทั้งสองใช้ <strong>Xendit-hosted page</strong> เพื่อการจัดการรายละเอียดการชำระเงินที่ปลอดภัยและเป็นไปตามมาตรฐาน PCI One-Time Payment เหมาะสำหรับการชำระเงินทันทีที่ลูกค้าอยู่ต่อหน้า ในขณะที่ Save Payment Method ช่วยให้สามารถทำธุรกรรมในอนาคตได้โดยไม่ต้องให้ลูกค้าป้อนรายละเอียดการชำระเงินซ้ำ</p></section><p data-block-id=\"mgfw1jv6-hist0g-007\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfw1khd-wlvnwt-008\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfw1fmt-3iwt10-005\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfw1ggn-okwf67-006\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvr4st-plopvz-022\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvr5dv-v7x4k6-023\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvo6vv-sudkp8-005\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvr0li-fvgiry-021\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvmk4k-sszmsg-036\"></p><div text=\"Loading text...\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfvnqcj-kappnr-002\"></p></div><p data-block-id=\"mgfv8aac-przgwj-022\"></p><p data-block-id=\"8b5e8486-5b19-4596-956f-3e52d4efc952\"></p>","SeoTitle":"วิธีการทำงานของเซสชันการชำระเงิน","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Cómo funcionan las Payment Sessions","Slug":"how-payment-sessions-work","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"2f2862c9-22ca-4658-a12f-34a895b0f321\">Nuestros endpoints de Payment Session son soluciones para simplificar el proceso de recaudación de pagos o la gestión de la información del método de pago de su cliente final para su negocio. Esta funcionalidad aprovecha nuestra página alojada por Xendit para almacenar de forma segura los detalles de pago del cliente final, lo que facilita futuras transacciones.</p><p data-block-id=\"f94ce33c-f510-445f-b5d1-73309cff6ff9\"><img data-block-id=\"mhlkyrfg-pcs3d3-001\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(144).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"3359aed2-87e0-4a45-b7cb-1f06dee77506\" class=\"sl-link-heading sl-text-4xl sl-leading-tight sl-font-prose sl-font-bold sl-text-heading\" id=\"how-does-it-work\" style=\"text-align:start;line-height:1.33333;box-sizing:border-box;border:0 solid var(--color-border,currentColor);--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-inset:var(--tw-empty,/*!*/ /*!*/);--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(147,197,253,0.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;margin:1.428em 0px 1em;font-size:1.75em;font-weight:700;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;color:rgb(38, 38, 38);font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\"><strong>Resumen de la solución</strong></h2><p data-block-id=\"d59640b6-5e90-4ba3-8048-8cd8b069a6fd\"><img data-block-id=\"647ff642-d876-477e-8a48-c90759dcc7f0\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Untitled diagram-2024-12-03-123511.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><h4 data-block-id=\"71e69fd0-833e-4aca-8f52-c7e4ae39972e\">Cómo funciona:</h4><ol data-block-id=\"b72e53bf-a10e-4527-a478-8e812e552fde\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"bca1ad23-a78f-4b84-9c1a-631276c569a7\"><p data-block-id=\"00381c81-9d26-4326-8642-0cde96f31e5e\">Cuando su cliente acepta guardar su método de pago para futuros cargos, cree un <strong>Payment Session API</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"b7ecc48d-91d8-4391-9a01-e1cb98485ad1\"><p data-block-id=\"e51deb38-ef95-4b12-8ffb-d6b14304f39b\">Redirija al cliente a la <strong>payment link url</strong> proporcionada en la response de la sesión</p></li><li data-block-id=\"fdde03f5-458c-4992-a2b8-a307a5fdd392\"><p data-block-id=\"2284be67-2de7-43b1-a4f7-707eb5148175\">El cliente ingresa los detalles de su método de pago en la página alojada por Xendit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"778bf047-029d-40cf-858d-9014e7118952\"><p data-block-id=\"8132937c-7381-4a58-a1b1-e7c3ea4e2533\">Xendit envía un <strong>webhook</strong> a su sistema cuando el método de pago se vincula exitosamente</p></li><li data-block-id=\"cb15486e-c8c4-4995-bcb8-d678f5033718\"><p data-block-id=\"a81ac303-8b13-44b9-804e-5311e1f5c7b0\">Guarde el <code>Payment Token</code> del webhook. Este token se utilizará para futuras transacciones</p></li><li data-block-id=\"cd7edda4-da6c-4ad9-892a-c090ef3c61cf\"><p data-block-id=\"0e76828b-fc6a-423d-a0ef-393bd1e2224f\">Cuando sea el momento de cobrar al cliente, active un Payment Request utilizando el <code>Payment Token</code> almacenado (consulte esta <a href=\"/docs/pay-with-tokens\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">guía</a>)</p></li></ol><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\" data-permitted-reader-groups=\"9f0df790-187b-4514-b1da-ec79a03a5322\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfvo6vv-tmei9l-003\"><strong>Payment Session</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvofw3-h2myck-006\"><strong>Payment Session API</strong> es una solución simplificada para aceptar pagos y gestionar los métodos de pago de sus clientes a través de una <strong>página de checkout alojada por Xendit</strong>.<br type=\"inline\">Le permite recaudar pagos únicos con el cliente presente o guardar de forma segura el método de pago de un cliente para uso futuro, todo con un esfuerzo de integración mínimo.</p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvou0i-54nfqw-010\" data-start=\"539\" data-end=\"582\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvou0i-54nfqw-010\" data-start=\"539\" data-end=\"582\">Payment Session admite tres casos de uso clave:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mgfvou0i-pqnd65-011\" data-start=\"584\" data-end=\"768\"><li data-block-id=\"mgfvou0i-gd6plz-012\" data-start=\"584\" data-end=\"666\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfvou0j-opbimn-013\" data-start=\"586\" data-end=\"666\"><mark class=\"0a28e540-605d-486a-b0f7-2959adf4698b\" data-type=\"comment\" data-comment-id=\"0a28e540-605d-486a-b0f7-2959adf4698b\"><strong>One-Time Payment</strong></mark> – Recaude un solo pago donde el cliente está presente.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfvou0j-efkvtz-014\" data-start=\"667\" data-end=\"768\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfvou0j-eoviec-015\" data-start=\"669\" data-end=\"768\"><strong>Save Payment Method</strong> – Permita a los clientes guardar de forma segura su método de pago para futuras transacciones.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfvou0j-efkvtz-014\" data-start=\"667\" data-end=\"768\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfvou0j-eoviec-015\" data-start=\"669\" data-end=\"768\"><strong>Pay and Save</strong> – Recaude el pago y guarde la información de pago del cliente final al mismo tiempo en un flujo combinado.</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mgfvou0j-gva9zb-016\" data-start=\"770\" data-end=\"890\">Todas las Payment Sessions utilizan una página de checkout alojada por Xendit para garantizar experiencias de usuario seguras, conformes y consistentes.</p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvqf26-koz0pn-017\" data-start=\"770\" data-end=\"890\"><img data-block-id=\"mgfvyxoz-f5xhhd-003\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(144).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvqkkd-arhbep-019\" data-start=\"770\" data-end=\"890\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvqkwc-qyekrz-020\" data-start=\"770\" data-end=\"890\"><strong>Resumen de la Solución</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfw1oa3-mbf1kx-009\"><img data-block-id=\"mhko9y4o-mc4r0r-001\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Untitled diagram-2025-11-04-103337.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mhketkze-rlrllb-008\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfw1oa3-mbf1kx-009\">Payment Session simplifica la recaudación de pagos y la gestión de métodos de pago a través de una <strong>página de checkout alojada por Xendit</strong>. Dependiendo de su caso de uso, el flujo puede ser <strong>One-Time Payment</strong>, <strong>Save Payment Method</strong> o <strong>Pay and Save</strong>.</p><ol data-block-id=\"mgfw5jd6-u8ndr9-153\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7r-ij9dh9-123\" data-start=\"260\" data-end=\"449\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7r-eo8452-124\" data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"293\">Cree una Payment Session desde su servidor para un One-Time Payment o para Save Payment Method para obtener la <code data-start=\"433\" data-end=\"446\">payment_link_url</code> de Xendit.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7r-ncs7jx-130\" data-start=\"451\" data-end=\"590\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7r-7h5ta8-131\" data-start=\"454\" data-end=\"477\">Redirija a su cliente a la página alojada por Xendit utilizando la <code data-start=\"521\" data-end=\"539\">payment_link_url</code>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7r-e9yayp-135\" data-start=\"592\" data-end=\"693\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7r-ggt4s7-136\" data-start=\"595\" data-end=\"616\">El cliente ingresará los detalles de pago y confirmará la transacción dentro de la página de checkout alojada por Xendit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-2xvwla-140\" data-start=\"695\" data-end=\"1036\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-9g1xot-141\" data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"716\">Flujo de Pago</p><ul data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-ob0ftq-142\" data-start=\"720\" data-end=\"1036\"><li data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-09jkqi-143\" data-start=\"720\" data-end=\"868\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-qvy236-144\" data-start=\"722\" data-end=\"868\">One-Time Payment: Xendit procesa el pago y envía un webhook (<code data-start=\"794\" data-end=\"813\">payment.capture</code> o <code data-start=\"817\" data-end=\"833\">payment.failed</code>). Su sistema actualiza la orden.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-nnxjb6-145\" data-start=\"872\" data-end=\"1036\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-aisudl-146\" data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"1036\">Save Payment Method: Xendit vincula el método de pago y envía un webhook (<code data-start=\"952\" data-end=\"975\">payment_token.activation</code>). Su sistema almacena el Payment Token para futuros cargos.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-nnxjb6-145\" data-start=\"872\" data-end=\"1036\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw5e7s-aisudl-146\" data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"1036\">Pay and Save Method: Xendit procesa el pago y vincula el método de pago para un pago exitoso (<code data-start=\"794\" data-end=\"813\">payment.capture</code>&amp;<code data-start=\"952\" data-end=\"975\">payment_token.activation</code>, y <code>payment.failed</code>). Su sistema actualiza la orden y almacena el Payment Token para futuros cargos.</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-4jsali-052\" data-start=\"1547\" data-end=\"1817\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-qtcags-053\" data-start=\"1550\" data-end=\"1605\">Cargos Futuros (Opcional para Pay and Save y Save Payment Method)</p><ul data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-8sfigl-054\" data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1817\"><li data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-7l72hb-055\" data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1708\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-ys9998-056\" data-start=\"1611\" data-end=\"1708\">Cuando esté listo para cobrar al cliente, cree un <a href=\"/docs/pay-with-tokens\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">Payment Request utilizando el Payment Token almacenado.</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-qcr2ig-057\" data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1817\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-t4xvda-058\" data-start=\"1714\" data-end=\"1817\">El cliente no necesita volver a ingresar los detalles de pago, lo que simplifica los pagos recurrentes o repetidos.</p></li></ul></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mgfw25sy-oqgse3-059\" data-start=\"1819\" data-end=\"2112\"><strong>Notas Clave</strong>: Ambos flujos utilizan una <strong>página alojada por Xendit</strong> para el manejo seguro y compatible con PCI de los detalles de pago. One-Time Payment es ideal para pagos inmediatos con el cliente presente, Save Payment Method permite futuras transacciones sin requerir que el cliente vuelva a ingresar los detalles de pago, y Pay and Save es adecuado para transacciones inmediatas y permite futuras transacciones con los mismos detalles de pago en una sola vez.</p></section><p data-block-id=\"mgfw1jv6-hist0g-007\"></p><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\"><p data-block-id=\"mhket4ih-kp41pz-004\"><strong>Notas privadas - Archivo de Diagrama Mermaid</strong><br type=\"inline\"><br type=\"inline\">Versión anterior</p><p data-block-id=\"mhkoh0jg-3x4qwn-002\"><img data-block-id=\"mhkoh0uy-co48t1-003\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(143).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><pre data-block-id=\"mhketev5-347ipm-007\" language=\"plaintext\" data-custom-title=\"Custom\" class=\"language-plaintext\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\" spellcheck=\"false\">sequenceDiagram\n    participant Customer\n    participant ClientApp as Client App\n    participant ClientServer as Client Server\n    participant XenditServer as Xendit Server\n    participant XenditPage as Xendit Hosted Page\n\n    %% Step 1 - Create Payment Session\n    \n    note over ClientServer, XenditServer: Step 1 – Create Payment Session\n    ClientApp -&gt;&gt; ClientServer: Create Payment Session (One-Time or Save Payment Method)\n    ClientServer -&gt;&gt; XenditServer: Create Payment Session (API Request)\n    XenditServer --&gt;&gt; ClientServer: Return payment_link_url\n    ClientServer --&gt;&gt; ClientApp: Return payment_link_url\n    \n\n    %% Step 2 - Redirect Customer\n    note over Customer, ClientApp: Step 2 – Redirect Customer\n    ClientApp --&gt;&gt; Customer: Redirect customer to payment_link_url\n    Customer -&gt;&gt; XenditPage: Open Xendit-hosted checkout page\n    \n\n    %% Step 3 - Customer Action\n    note over Customer, XenditPage: Step 3 – Customer Action\n    Customer -&gt;&gt; XenditPage: Enter payment details and confirm\n    alt One-Time Payment\n        XenditPage -&gt;&gt; XenditServer: Process payment\n        XenditServer --&gt;&gt; ClientServer: Send webhook (payment.capture or payment.failed)\n        ClientServer -&gt;&gt; ClientServer: Update order or payment status\n    else Save Payment Method\n        XenditPage -&gt;&gt; XenditServer: Send payment method information\n        XenditServer --&gt;&gt; ClientServer: Send webhook (payment_token.activation)\n        ClientServer -&gt;&gt; ClientServer: Store Payment Token for future transactions\n    else Pay and Save\n        XenditPage -&gt;&gt; XenditServer: Process payment\n        XenditServer --&gt;&gt; ClientServer: Send webhook (payment.capture and payment_token.activation or payment.failed)\n        ClientServer -&gt;&gt; ClientServer: Update order or payment status\n\n    end\n</code></pre></section><p data-block-id=\"mhket4ih-rzpvhd-006\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfw1fmt-3iwt10-005\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfw1ggn-okwf67-006\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvr4st-plopvz-022\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvr5dv-v7x4k6-023\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvo6vv-sudkp8-005\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvr0li-fvgiry-021\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mgfvmk4k-sszmsg-036\"></p><div text=\"Loading text...\"><p data-block-id=\"mgfvnqcj-kappnr-002\"></p></div><p data-block-id=\"mgfv8aac-przgwj-022\"></p><p data-block-id=\"8b5e8486-5b19-4596-956f-3e52d4efc952\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Cómo funcionan las Payment Sessions","Description":null}]